==============================================================================

To finish setting up FidoLogin:

1. Ensure you have flash messages in app/views/layouts/application.html.erb,
   and a div on the page has the class 'fidologin-status' for JavaScript to
   display error messages in. For example:

      <p class="notice"><%= notice %></p>
      <p class="alert fidologin-status"><%= alert %></p>

==============================================================================
